        {
            "filters": [
                {
                    "test": "is_sleeping",
                    "value": true
                }
            ],
            "event": "minecraft:ambient_sleep"
        },
        {
            "filters": {
                "all_of": [
                    {
                        "test": "is_daytime",
                        "value": false
                    },
                    {
                        "test": "distance_to_nearest_player",
                        "operator": ">",
                        "value": 16
                    }
                ]
            },
            "event": "minecraft:ambient_night"
        },
        {
            "filters": {
                "all_of": [
                    {
                        "test": "is_sleeping",
                        "value": false
                    },
                    {
                        "any_of": [
                            {
                                "test": "is_daytime",
                                "value": true
                            },
                            {
                                "test": "distance_to_nearest_player",
                                "operator": "<=",
                                "value": 16
                            }
                        ]
                    }
                ]
            },
            "event": "minecraft:ambient_normal"
        }
    ]
}
